WEBVTT

1
00:15:18.260 --> 00:15:20.570 
代理人和女婿
and son-in-law of our local milord.

2
00:15:20.570 --> 00:15:22.290 
我都不知道我这么有名
I'm surprised I'm so famous.

3
00:15:22.600 --> 00:15:24.700 
你不准备为你的原则辩护吗
Won't you defend your principles?

4
00:15:24.700 --> 00:15:26.040 
不  这会儿不了
No, not now.

5
00:15:26.530 --> 00:15:29.630 
那我来  布兰森先生是个热忱的政治思考家
Then I will. Mr Branson is a keen political thinker.

6
00:15:29.890 --> 00:15:33.050 
他敢于质疑自己的信仰就证明了这一点
He proves this by not being afraid to question his own beliefs.

7
00:15:33.050 --> 00:15:33.930 
很有说服力
Very eloquent.

8
00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:37.660 
我很想留下来辩论一番  但是我要迟到了
I'd stay to argue, but I'm late.

9
00:15:39.240 --> 00:15:40.500 
你住在这附近吗
Do you live around here?

10
00:15:41.380 --> 00:15:42.620 
我在这儿工作
I work here.

11
00:15:43.010 --> 00:15:44.040 
在学校
At the school.

12
00:15:44.730 --> 00:15:46.250 
很高兴再见到你
It was nice to see you again.

